1.00	Slaughterer	The Edge Chronicles	The Edge Chronicles is a young-adult fantasy novel series by Paul Stewart and Chris Riddell. It consists of three trilogies, plus three additional books, and others (more than 13 books). Originally published in the United Kingdom, this series has since been published in the United States, Canada and Australia. To date, more than ten million copies of the novels have been sold. The fictional places and characters in the books are described, below, using in-universe tone of writing.	
